10.19.22  10:27 am   i want to get better at playing piano with two hands. any tips?

      whichever hand you're less good with, keep the keyboard on that side. if you're worse with your left hand, keep your keyboard to the left side of your desk. another fun practice trick is to try playing for a while with only certain fingers. maybe just 1 finger on each hand. or maybe 2 fingers on your worse hand and 1 on your better hand. just remember to keep it to just 1 whenever you get into the bass range, unless you like mud slop
